{"tid":1507474,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【催淚彈正名為化學武器「山埃彈」】荃新天地外施放嘅催淚彈，山埃讀數超標","createTime":"2019-08-26T07:18:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T17:36:41.000Z","uid":79563,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c1a4a49cf0eb4abdfda3fefb390a6ed4a99db6ff","tid":1507474,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T07:18:36.000Z","msg":"【荃灣現場編委報導】<br />\n[17:54] 警方稍早前於荃新天地外施放多枚催淚彈。本會記者使用可測試氰化氫（俗稱山埃）之儀器上前測試，發現讀數超標，片中可見儀器不斷發出聲響。如市民短時間內吸入高濃度氰化氫氣體，嚴重可導致停止呼吸而死亡。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hsusueb/videos/667645400420901/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhsusueb%2Fvideos%2F667645400420901%2F&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTY1EyhmTkDJ%2BTCVbHNRNdZc8%3D&h=6e31df0e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hsusueb/videos/667645400420901/</a><br />\n<br />\nFrom 香港恒生大學學生會編輯委員會 Editorial Board, HSUSU"},{"pid":"c7f8ac74a951d992692ec5c1a76615099c3b148e","tid":1507474,"uid":33930,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T07:18:58.000Z","msg":"唔好意思借個post宣傳一下<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4GJMrJb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4GJMrJb.jpg&h=cb7c9807&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n901 和你塞  13:00 見   <a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTY1EyhmTkDJ%2BTCVbHNRNdZc8%3D&h=8f676875\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a>"},{"pid":"07517a623e85236b825000cfaa982568f176ce49","tid":1507474,"uid":185990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T07:19:24.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n集思廣益  對付白色恐怖嘅方法<br />